{"id": "1293964313979261051", "channel_id": "1293860297731215431", "type": 19, "author_id": "1254117831289737258", "author_name": "tululike", "author_bot": false, "content": "有12叠巨人和专武的情况下强效爆伤该怎么已经分配啊？", "timestamp": "2024-10-10T15:52:13.147000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1226317601831911467"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1293871108621074495", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293860297731215431", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血链·希洛的抽取建议", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777"]}
{"id": "1293964557584306329", "channel_id": "1293860297731215431", "type": 19, "author_id": "1226317601831911467", "author_name": "tranquil_monkey_73179", "author_bot": false, "content": "自己算吧哈哈\n我做攻略从来没拉过表的\n因为双爆都可以靠造物补\n自己决定吧", "timestamp": "2024-10-10T15:53:11.227000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1254117831289737258"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1293964313979261051", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293860297731215431", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血链·希洛的抽取建议", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777"]}
{"id": "1294049246680715385", "channel_id": "1293860297731215431", "type": 19, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "我的建议是，你洗的时候，出爆伤和强效其中一条满的你就锁1开洗，剩下的看你运气，给爆伤你就留爆伤，给强效你就留强效，然后强效低了的情况下，你三个辅助队友的密契可以主堆强效", "timestamp": "2024-10-10T21:29:42.681000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1254117831289737258"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1293964313979261051", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293860297731215431", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血链·希洛的抽取建议", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777"]}
{"id": "1294049517414649886", "channel_id": "1293860297731215431", "type": 0, "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "author_bot": false, "content": "希洛的爆伤乘区其实给的很大方，打击给，然后超限那个还是永久的，但是强效你只能靠自己的练度，但是刻意去追求极限，造价太高了，洗出什么用什么比较好", "timestamp": "2024-10-10T21:30:47.229000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293860297731215431", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血链·希洛的抽取建议", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777"]}
